To install:

```
git clone --recurse-submodules https://github.com/galtrhan/.dotfiles ~/.dotfiles
cd ~/.dotfiles
stow .
```

Optional install script:

```
chmod +x install.sh
./install.sh
```

### Requirements
- hyprland
- hyprpaper
- hypridle
- hyprlock
- waybar
- kitty
- tmux
- neovim
- stow



